{"tid":538822,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【山寨GDP】LV、Rolex、Cartier乜都有 深圳掃逾3800件假貨","createTime":"2018-01-24T03:39:45.000Z","updateTime":"2018-01-24T03:58:24.000Z","uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"5fd42aaece58ed8434ff82e788c036435374a18a","tid":538822,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-24T03:39:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20180124/large/1516757716_4f1f.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20180124%2Flarge%2F1516757716_4f1f.jpg&h=4f6ce97b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n冒牌貨在深圳相當盛行，深圳市市場和質量監管委羅湖局近日在區內巡查，在水貝、東門等地起出大批冒牌貨，當中包括LV、Gucci冒牌皮具，Rolex、OMEGA、Longines等冒牌手錶，超過3,800件。<br />\n<br />\n當局指出，本月9日當局派員到2間位於水貝的飾品店進行突擊檢查。現場查獲假冒Cartier、梵克雅寶（Van Cleef &amp; Arpels）等名牌飾品2,057件。同日，當局又派員到東門一間兒童服裝巡查，起出冒牌Hello Kitty兒童內褲1,284條。<br />\n<br />\n當局在上周三（17日）再派人到東門步行街巡查，在一個倉庫中起出包括LV、Gucci等品牌皮具，假冒Longines、OMEGA、Rolex等品牌手錶共500多件。<br />\n<br />\n目前當局已將當中<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">9案件</span></span></strong>立案偵查。<br />\n<br />\n深圳新聞網"},{"pid":"cf7b0ecda4b27c0b2a3444a81fb4f67dc31cfd2b","tid":538822,"uid":42188,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-24T03:41:00.000Z","msg":"呢9間鋪無俾錢政府<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3ccbc41c82bfa6a0f4219404f81d9e5f012ce2fe","tid":538822,"uid":61105,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-24T03:47:10.000Z","msg":"佢地應該係做緊5000蚊黨主席個任務<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e5d811e51bd36e0922475f7ec1a25b5c393b1dd1","tid":538822,"uid":77196,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"3ccbc41c82bfa6a0f4219404f81d9e5f012ce2fe","tid":538822,"uid":61105,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-24T03:47:10.000Z","msg":"佢地應該係做緊5000蚊黨主席個任務<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgm